# --- LuckyWheelPublic (گردونه عمومی) — بدون Auth ---

### دریافت اطلاعات گردونه
GET {{Api_Vapp_HostAddress}}/api/LuckyWheelPublic/norooz-wheel

### چرخش گردونه
POST {{Api_Vapp_HostAddress}}/api/LuckyWheelPublic/norooz-wheel/spin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantFullName": "سارا محمدی",
  "participantMobile": "09123334455"
}

